casebody.data:
Aspetuck Valley Country Club, Inc. v. A & B Wood Design Associates, Inc. (11665)

Daly, O’Connell and Lavery, Js.

Argued May 7 decision released June 8, 1993 Michael J. McCabe, with whom, on the brief, was Christopher J. Lutzo, law student intern, for the appellant (plaintiff). *926Mario P. Musilli, with whom, on the brief, was Lisa B. Kouzoujian, for the appellee (defendant). Per Curiam.

The judgment is affirmed.
